me.desht.sensibletoolbox.api

Interface EnderTunable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnderBag, EnderBox

    public interface EnderTunable
    Represents an STB item or block which has an ender frequency including global/personal visibility.

    • Method Summary

    • Method Detail

      • getEnderFrequency

        int getEnderFrequency()
        Get the ender frequency of this tunable object.
        Returns:
        the object's current ender frequency

      • setEnderFrequency

        void setEnderFrequency(int frequency)
        Change the ender frequency of this tunable object.
        Parameters:
        frequency - the new ender frequency

      • isGlobal

        boolean isGlobal()
        Check if this object is on a global or personal frequency. Global frequency indicates that the inventory is common to all players; personal frequency indicates that the inventory is separate for each player accessing this object.
        Returns:
        true if this a global frequency; false otherwise

      • setGlobal

        void setGlobal(boolean global)
        Define whether this tunable object should be on a global or personal frequency.
        Parameters:
        global - true if this should be a global frequency; false otherwise
